":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8088864?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62","html_url":"https://github.com/hankliu62","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"open_issues":17,"closed_issues":0,"state":"open","created_at":"2024-03-20T03:36:14Z","updated_at":"2024-04-19T04:10:46Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":null},"comments":0,"created_at":"2024-04-19T04:10:46Z","updated_at":"2024-04-19T04:10:46Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"事件冒泡是基于 DOM 树结构以及事件捕获和事件冒泡两种事件传播机制的原理。\r\n\r\n1. **DOM 树结构：** 在浏览器中，HTML 文档以 DOM 树的形式表示，每个 HTML 元素都是树中的节点。这些节点按照其嵌套关系形成了父子关系。\r\n\r\n2. **事件捕获和事件冒泡：** 浏览器中的事件传播机制分为两种方式：事件捕获和事件冒泡。\r\n   - **事件捕获：** 事件首先从根节点向目标节点传播，沿着 DOM 树的上行阶段进行。即事件会从最外层的祖先节点一直传播到目标节点。\r\n   - **事件冒泡：** 事件从目标节点向根节点传播，沿着 DOM 树的下行阶段进行。即事件会从目标节点一直传播到最外层的祖先节点。\r\n\r\n事件冒泡是基于事件在 DOM 树中向上传播的原理。当一个元素触发了某个事件（比如点击事件），该事件会依次向上冒泡到该元素的父级元素，直到根节点。这个过程中，父级元素上绑定的相同类型的事件处理函数都会被依次调用。\r\n\r\n因此，事件冒泡机制使得我们可以在父级元素上统一管理和处理子元素的事件，实现事件委托、代码优化和性能提升的目的。\r\n","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/617/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/617/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason